    "romaji": "'Nihongo no Kyoushitsu' Kayoubi to mokuyoubi ni arimasu. Kayoubi wa gozen juuji kara juuni-ji made desu. Mokuyoubi wa gogo niji kara yoji made desu. Basho wa toshokan no nikai desu.",
